g.text: 3.1: The System confirms the Payment and informs the collaborator about the success of the operation.
2.2: The System presents the amount that he has to pay.
1.2: The System request for necessary input(brief description of the task,
information about the Freelancer that worked on the task).
1: The Collaborator starts the payment process.
